org.sql: SELECT DISTINCT notes.* FROM notes INNER JOIN note_comments ON notes.id = note_comments.note_id WHERE note_comments.author_id = "$1" ORDER BY updated_at DESC, id LIMIT "$2" OFFSET "$3"
